WEBVTT

00:00:10.359 --> 00:00:10.960
Here

00:00:11.880 --> 00:00:12.560
Mom

00:00:13.479 --> 00:00:13.920
Here

00:00:14.359 --> 00:00:15.760
Have a chicken wing

00:00:19.760 --> 00:00:21.360
Looks like you've grown wings too

00:00:21.959 --> 00:00:22.920
Such a dangerous operation

00:00:22.920 --> 00:00:24.799
and you just went along with it

00:00:25.239 --> 00:00:26.520
Aren't I perfectly fine

00:00:26.520 --> 00:00:27.600
sitting here eating now?

00:00:28.920 --> 00:00:30.600
Besides, your sweetheart is so sharp

00:00:30.879 --> 00:00:31.879
I'm telling you

00:00:32.479 --> 00:00:34.080
Your dad is already like that

00:00:35.040 --> 00:00:37.319
You want me to worry about one more person?

00:00:41.560 --> 00:00:42.360
Mom

00:00:43.639 --> 00:00:44.799
Calm down, please

00:00:45.599 --> 00:00:46.479
I promise

00:00:47.479 --> 00:00:48.599
if there's ever a next time

00:00:48.880 --> 00:00:49.959
I'll be more careful

00:00:51.119 --> 00:00:52.400
You want there to be a next time?

00:00:52.840 --> 00:00:53.680
There won't be

00:00:56.680 --> 00:00:57.479
Mom

00:00:58.040 --> 00:00:59.119
Let me ask you something

00:01:00.720 --> 00:01:01.959
Do you still remember

00:01:02.479 --> 00:01:04.120
before something happened to my dad

00:01:04.639 --> 00:01:06.360
was anything off about him?

00:01:06.839 --> 00:01:08.440
I only remember that back then

00:01:09.160 --> 00:01:10.959
he suddenly got very busy

00:01:12.720 --> 00:01:14.519
and mysteriously told me

00:01:14.720 --> 00:01:16.400
if anything happened to him

00:01:16.639 --> 00:01:17.839
to take good care of you

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:22.360
At that time

00:01:22.360 --> 00:01:24.879
he often snuck out at night

00:01:25.360 --> 00:01:26.239
I almost thought

00:01:26.239 --> 00:01:27.919
he had someone else outside

00:01:31.440 --> 00:01:32.440
At that time, he

00:01:32.879 --> 00:01:34.239
got a phone call

00:01:35.239 --> 00:01:37.120
and then hurried out

00:01:37.720 --> 00:01:39.080
No idea who called

00:01:42.720 --> 00:01:44.760
Why tell me this only now?

00:01:45.279 --> 00:01:46.800
You were fishing for this, weren't you?

00:01:46.879 --> 00:01:48.480
How many times have I told you

00:01:48.480 --> 00:01:50.040
your dad is never waking up

00:01:50.040 --> 00:01:52.279
Are you ignoring everything I say?

00:02:01.879 --> 00:02:02.599
Mom

00:02:03.120 --> 00:02:04.839
I hope you can support me

00:02:05.080 --> 00:02:06.360
Even if you don't support me

00:02:07.040 --> 00:02:08.479
don't stand in my way

00:02:09.360 --> 00:02:10.600
Look at my dad

00:02:11.080 --> 00:02:12.479
He's just lying there

00:02:13.759 --> 00:02:15.240
I've never again heard him personally

00:02:15.240 --> 00:02:16.720
call me sweetheart

00:02:17.000 --> 00:02:18.800
My dad was a lawyer all his life

00:02:18.880 --> 00:02:21.000
He won cases for so many vulnerable people

00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:22.240
But what about him now?

00:02:22.639 --> 00:02:24.160
Now he's lying in a coma

00:02:24.160 --> 00:02:25.479
and was framed for taking bribes

00:02:26.320 --> 00:02:27.759
But the person who caused all this

00:02:27.759 --> 00:02:28.919
is still out there free

00:02:30.839 --> 00:02:32.039
I can't just

00:02:32.039 --> 00:02:33.679
watch all this happen

00:02:34.919 --> 00:02:35.759
I will definitely

00:02:37.880 --> 00:02:39.240
find out the truth

00:02:46.960 --> 00:02:47.759
Mom

00:02:49.600 --> 00:02:50.800
Work's been busy lately

00:02:51.679 --> 00:02:52.880
so I won't be coming back to stay for now

00:02:54.960 --> 00:02:56.000
You must take good care of yourself

00:02:56.000 --> 00:02:56.880
and my dad too

00:03:18.639 --> 00:03:20.000
I heard a new person is joining the team

00:03:20.880 --> 00:03:21.559
Who is it?

00:03:22.639 --> 00:03:23.839
I'm telling you

00:03:24.039 --> 00:03:25.240
It's definitely Lu Yi

00:03:25.240 --> 00:03:25.960
Right

00:03:27.199 --> 00:03:28.479
Lu Yi is joining our squad

00:03:28.479 --> 00:03:29.600
Has she already arrived?

00:03:30.279 --> 00:03:31.839
I saw her in the office building

00:03:32.919 --> 00:03:33.320
Captain

00:03:34.039 --> 00:03:35.160
Why agree to transfer her here?

00:03:36.440 --> 00:03:38.039
I think Lu Yi is pretty good

00:03:38.880 --> 00:03:40.000
She's quick on the uptake

00:03:40.199 --> 00:03:41.160
and very attentive

00:03:41.960 --> 00:03:43.440
Let's give young people a

00:03:43.440 --> 00:03:44.399
chance to grow

00:03:44.399 --> 00:03:45.199
What's wrong?

00:03:51.479 --> 00:03:53.479
You did well on this mission

00:03:54.119 --> 00:03:55.679
You've got what it takes to be a detective

00:03:57.360 --> 00:03:58.160
As for your dad

00:03:58.759 --> 00:04:00.360
I can finally give some account

00:04:02.160 --> 00:04:03.839
Director Zheng, you flatter me

00:04:04.279 --> 00:04:06.160
You and my dad go way back too

00:04:06.360 --> 00:04:07.679
These past years since my dad's accident

00:04:07.919 --> 00:04:09.119
you've really looked after us

00:04:09.639 --> 00:04:10.320
Don't worry

00:04:10.679 --> 00:04:11.839
I'll definitely work hard

00:04:11.960 --> 00:04:13.080
I won't let you down

00:04:14.199 --> 00:04:15.000
That's the spirit

00:04:15.960 --> 00:04:16.679
Reporting in

00:04:16.679 --> 00:04:17.480
Come in

00:04:21.760 --> 00:04:22.279
Director Zheng

00:04:23.000 --> 00:04:23.679
Lin Shen

00:04:24.079 --> 00:04:24.760
You came at the right time

00:04:25.359 --> 00:04:27.119
This is Lu Yi, our new team member

00:04:27.119 --> 00:04:28.600
Show her around and get her settled in

00:04:29.679 --> 00:04:30.279
No need

00:04:30.399 --> 00:04:31.279
I know this place well

00:04:32.079 --> 00:04:32.760
Director Zheng

00:04:33.079 --> 00:04:34.359
I have something to report to you

00:04:34.440 --> 00:04:34.920
All right

00:04:35.959 --> 00:04:36.559
Lu Yi

00:04:37.000 --> 00:04:37.600
Then you

00:04:37.600 --> 00:04:39.040
go find Captain Duan first

00:04:39.799 --> 00:04:40.359
Got it

00:04:41.679 --> 00:04:42.959
Then Director Zheng, I'll head out first

00:05:01.040 --> 00:05:02.279
What's going on, Lei ge?

00:05:02.959 --> 00:05:03.720
There's a story there, huh?

00:05:11.720 --> 00:05:13.760
Do you know about that cold case from our bureau years ago

00:05:14.480 --> 00:05:15.720
The No. 13 Middle School Murder Case

00:05:16.600 --> 00:05:17.600
That lawyer, Lu Yong

00:05:18.279 --> 00:05:19.320
One time, First Team

00:05:19.320 --> 00:05:20.679
was catching a fugitive near No. 13 Middle School

00:05:20.880 --> 00:05:22.160
just as they were about to wrap up

00:05:22.559 --> 00:05:23.679
they realized Big Guy had vanished

00:05:24.200 --> 00:05:25.399
In the storage room at No. 13 Middle School

00:05:25.399 --> 00:05:26.600
when they found Big Guy

00:05:26.720 --> 00:05:27.799
he had already been shot

00:05:28.519 --> 00:05:29.200
He was dead

00:05:30.079 --> 00:05:31.359
There were also two bodies lying beside him

00:05:32.839 --> 00:05:34.399
There was one more very strange thing

00:05:34.640 --> 00:05:35.640
Someone showed up at the scene

00:05:35.640 --> 00:05:37.119
who should not have been there

00:05:37.279 --> 00:05:38.119
It was Lu Yong

00:05:38.559 --> 00:05:39.040
A lawyer

00:05:39.040 --> 00:05:39.679
No one knew why

00:05:39.679 --> 00:05:40.920
he just happened to be there

00:05:41.679 --> 00:05:43.239
with a large sum of money on him

00:05:44.920 --> 00:05:45.959
Could it be

00:05:46.640 --> 00:05:48.000
that the fugitive did it

00:05:48.399 --> 00:05:49.200
No

00:05:49.559 --> 00:05:50.880
At the arrest scene, there was also

00:05:50.880 --> 00:05:51.760
another murder

00:05:52.440 --> 00:05:54.000
Maybe Lu Yong and Big Guy

00:05:54.000 --> 00:05:55.239
walked in on the murder

00:05:56.559 --> 00:05:57.959
but no one knows what exactly happened

00:05:59.320 --> 00:06:00.760
So Lu Yi's dad also

00:06:00.760 --> 00:06:01.160
didn't make it

00:06:01.720 --> 00:06:02.760
Only Big Guy was killed

00:06:04.519 --> 00:06:06.119
The only witness, Lu Yong, fell into a coma

00:06:06.920 --> 00:06:08.000
But it was later confirmed

00:06:08.440 --> 00:06:09.760
that the bullet type found in Big Guy

00:06:09.760 --> 00:06:11.320
matched his own service weapon

00:06:11.600 --> 00:06:13.119
But that gun mysteriously disappeared

00:06:13.359 --> 00:06:14.519
And the killer was never found

00:06:16.239 --> 00:06:17.600
Then how did Lu Yi become a cop

00:06:20.279 --> 00:06:21.880
The scene had been cleaned up thoroughly

00:06:23.320 --> 00:06:25.480
The only witness, Lu Yong, stayed in a coma

00:06:26.640 --> 00:06:27.519
The case remained unsolved

00:06:27.519 --> 00:06:28.559
and there were all kinds of rumors

00:06:30.880 --> 00:06:32.640
They said that stack of cash in Lu Yong's pocket

00:06:33.279 --> 00:06:34.559
was slipped to him by the defendant

00:06:35.200 --> 00:06:36.000
In our bureau

00:06:36.519 --> 00:06:37.320
Stop right there

00:06:39.799 --> 00:06:41.959
Why are you talking nonsense about unproven things

00:06:42.640 --> 00:06:44.200
Is that a habit in our team

00:06:48.079 --> 00:06:48.760
Lu Yi

00:06:49.000 --> 00:06:49.959
before anything happened to her dad

00:06:49.959 --> 00:06:51.079
had already gotten into police academy

00:06:51.079 --> 00:06:52.279
After graduating, she was assigned to

00:06:52.279 --> 00:06:53.799
our South City Police Station

00:06:54.640 --> 00:06:56.559
And she did very well on this case

00:06:56.920 --> 00:06:58.119
She was transferred to our team

00:06:58.559 --> 00:06:59.359
Got it

00:07:00.440 --> 00:07:01.160
Got it

00:07:01.279 --> 00:07:02.079
Got it

00:07:02.880 --> 00:07:03.519
Back to work

00:07:11.399 --> 00:07:12.279
New recruit Xiao Lu

00:07:12.519 --> 00:07:13.399
reporting for duty

00:07:13.760 --> 00:07:14.399
Lu Yi

00:07:15.880 --> 00:07:16.839
Welcome, welcome

00:07:16.839 --> 00:07:18.519
Welcome to the Criminal Investigation Team

00:07:19.799 --> 00:07:20.640
Hello, Captain Duan

00:07:20.720 --> 00:07:22.040
To become one of your team members

00:07:22.040 --> 00:07:23.559
is truly such an honor for me

00:07:25.959 --> 00:07:26.720
You sure know what to say

00:07:27.720 --> 00:07:28.440
Hello, everyone

00:07:28.839 --> 00:07:29.720
Long time no see

00:07:30.200 --> 00:07:31.320
Starting today

00:07:31.679 --> 00:07:32.839
we are one family

00:07:33.200 --> 00:07:34.359
Please take good care of me

00:07:34.839 --> 00:07:35.279
Applause

00:07:35.279 --> 00:07:35.640
Alright

00:07:36.679 --> 00:07:37.399
Lu Yi

00:07:38.600 --> 00:07:39.679
your desk

00:07:40.000 --> 00:07:40.720
is right over there

00:07:41.279 --> 00:07:42.200
across from Lin Shen

00:07:42.720 --> 00:07:43.320
Alright

00:07:49.799 --> 00:07:51.040
One more thing

00:07:51.880 --> 00:07:53.880
I still need to ask for your help with something

00:07:54.160 --> 00:07:54.839
Go ahead then

00:07:54.839 --> 00:07:55.760
Well, you see

00:07:56.399 --> 00:07:58.519
I am homeless right now

00:07:58.640 --> 00:07:59.359
As for a place

00:07:59.359 --> 00:08:01.519
I cannot find one that quickly

00:08:03.519 --> 00:08:04.519
I heard

00:08:05.000 --> 00:08:06.399
Comrade Lin Shen

00:08:06.920 --> 00:08:08.920
you rent a place nearby, right

00:08:10.119 --> 00:08:10.640
Lin Shen

00:08:11.480 --> 00:08:13.559
I remember your place is pretty big

00:08:14.200 --> 00:08:15.679
There is room for a sofa bed too

00:08:15.880 --> 00:08:16.519
Right

00:08:16.760 --> 00:08:17.440
How about this

00:08:18.119 --> 00:08:18.720
Lu Yi

00:08:19.000 --> 00:08:20.399
can stay with you for now

00:08:20.399 --> 00:08:21.760
That way you can look out for each other

00:08:22.559 --> 00:08:23.359
No

00:08:24.640 --> 00:08:25.519
I do not think it is a good idea either

00:08:29.760 --> 00:08:30.920
What is it to you

00:08:31.320 --> 00:08:32.039
Stay out of it

00:08:35.000 --> 00:08:36.320
Then it is settled for now

00:08:36.640 --> 00:08:37.119
Lin Shen

00:08:37.440 --> 00:08:39.080
help Lu Yi sort out her luggage first

00:08:39.919 --> 00:08:42.039
Does what I say as captain not count anymore

00:08:42.200 --> 00:08:43.000
I was just

00:08:45.159 --> 00:08:46.599
Thank you, Comrade Lin Shen

00:08:47.239 --> 00:08:48.200
Thank you

00:08:49.599 --> 00:08:50.679
Then my luggage

00:08:50.679 --> 00:08:51.520
is in your hands

00:08:57.640 --> 00:08:58.719
Comrade Lin Shen

00:08:59.479 --> 00:09:01.640
Why does your place feel so cold

00:09:01.640 --> 00:09:03.159
It is like an operating room

00:09:03.679 --> 00:09:05.039
There is no homey feeling at all

00:09:06.559 --> 00:09:07.919
The bed I bought for you arrives tomorrow

00:09:09.679 --> 00:09:10.719
Change your shoes when you come in

00:09:15.640 --> 00:09:17.119
Hang your coat on the rack

00:09:17.119 --> 00:09:18.400
Clean up right after you eat

00:09:18.880 --> 00:09:19.640
After eleven o'clock

00:09:19.840 --> 00:09:20.799
you are not allowed to make any noise

00:09:25.520 --> 00:09:26.479
Some things

00:09:26.479 --> 00:09:28.039
should be seen from the bright side

00:09:28.320 --> 00:09:30.080
It is so much livelier with two people living together

00:09:30.080 --> 00:09:31.679
That way we can take care of each other

00:09:31.679 --> 00:09:32.520
help each other

00:09:32.520 --> 00:09:33.640
understand each other

00:09:34.159 --> 00:09:35.400
Maybe when we have free time

00:09:35.400 --> 00:09:37.039
we can discuss cases together more often

00:09:37.039 --> 00:09:38.599
and really solve cases well together

00:09:38.799 --> 00:09:39.599
Leg

00:09:40.320 --> 00:09:42.000
In the future we can

00:09:42.000 --> 00:09:45.200
be the two Sister Cops of our police team

00:09:47.599 --> 00:09:48.200
What are you doing

00:09:49.200 --> 00:09:50.520
There is no need to be this cruel

00:09:50.520 --> 00:09:52.080
I actually can stop talking

00:10:04.799 --> 00:10:05.760
What is this for

00:10:08.359 --> 00:10:09.440
Why are you putting this up

00:10:15.559 --> 00:10:16.359
Your hand

00:10:18.559 --> 00:10:19.320
Your hand

00:10:20.119 --> 00:10:20.719
Your hand

00:10:23.000 --> 00:10:24.200
Your hand crossed the Boundary line

00:10:25.359 --> 00:10:26.919
From now on, I stay here, you stay there

00:10:26.919 --> 00:10:27.760
No interfering with each other

00:10:27.880 --> 00:10:28.559
No bothering each other

00:10:30.479 --> 00:10:31.000
Come on

00:10:31.280 --> 00:10:32.840
How old are you, still doing a Boundary line?

00:10:32.840 --> 00:10:34.359
Do you ever get tired of this?

00:10:34.520 --> 00:10:35.719
Childish

00:10:37.479 --> 00:10:39.000
Boundary line

00:10:41.200 --> 00:10:42.239
I'm getting my pajamas

00:10:42.239 --> 00:10:43.080
Then beg me

00:10:43.760 --> 00:10:44.239
I...

00:10:45.000 --> 00:10:46.239
This is my home

00:10:53.559 --> 00:10:54.359
Which one?

00:10:57.559 --> 00:10:58.359
The blue one

00:11:01.280 --> 00:11:01.840
Here you go

00:11:49.520 --> 00:11:51.119
Sorry about that, Comrade Lin Shen

00:11:51.119 --> 00:11:53.200
I'm just kind of careless

00:11:53.200 --> 00:11:54.840
And I have a lot of stuff

00:11:55.039 --> 00:11:56.119
If you don't mind

00:11:56.119 --> 00:11:57.239
you can also show some of

00:11:57.239 --> 00:11:58.080
your helpful spirit

00:11:58.080 --> 00:11:58.840
I don't mind

00:12:00.679 --> 00:12:01.960
The room divider arrives tomorrow

00:12:01.960 --> 00:12:02.719
I'm a neat freak

00:12:02.719 --> 00:12:03.880
Hurry up and clean this up

00:12:22.719 --> 00:12:23.840
The person in the photo

00:12:24.359 --> 00:12:25.880
what exactly is their relation to Lin Shen?

00:12:26.640 --> 00:12:28.200
Is it really connected to my dad's case?

00:13:08.840 --> 00:13:10.359
With your little bit of skill,

00:13:10.679 --> 00:13:11.719
how are you going to catch a suspect?

00:13:11.719 --> 00:13:13.320
Well, I've still got you, don't I?

00:13:18.400 --> 00:13:20.000
From now on, I'll handle solving cases

00:13:20.000 --> 00:13:22.280
and you can handle catching suspects

00:13:22.280 --> 00:13:24.280
Two Sister Cops joining forces

00:13:32.000 --> 00:13:32.799
Where did the photo come from?